{"type":"text","timestamp":1781755592472,"sessionID":"ses_127185023ffen0qKKl1I08wyww","part":{"id":"prt_ed8e8a1af0016iMRXGIpL486fG","messageID":"msg_ed8e888cd001kO9gvNsCD3JVCE","sessionID":"ses_127185023ffen0qKKl1I08wyww","type":"text","text":"The workflow contract requires init state, one iteration, and synthesis artifacts. I’m checking the existing lineage directory and target packet inputs before writing anything, then I’ll create or update only the lineage packet files.","time":{"start":1781755584943,"end":1781755592469},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0b96872ad04e410d016a336ec0ef0c8191b32ed3934c2bee2a","phase":"commentary"}}}}
